Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Moynihan angry over UN's Zionist vote
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z98fn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Dec 1975
Daniel Moynihan, US ambassador to the UN, hits out over security council's Zionist vote. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less